---
title: Hoisin Chicken & Vegetable Tray Bake With Roasted Cashews
description: What’s as fuss free as going to your local Chinese restaurant…!? Not much, but we reckon this simple hoisin chicken bake comes close… It’s cooked in a jiffy, it’s big on flavour and best of all, the mess is minimal.
